"{\n  \"text\": \"Hey everybody, Scotty here. Uh, and I was at the farmer's market today selling some fermented foods, and uh this Hare Krishna guy came by and gave me a couple books, and it reminded me of the time when I was at yoga, and I got a free copy of the Bhagavad Gita or however the hell it's pronounced, and I read it because if a book drops into your life, you should read it. And it was amazing, and it's all about this guy who is about to lead these forces into this huge battle, and it's gonna kill everything and everybody and everyone he knows and all I mean it's just gonna be mass destruction. He didn't want to do it. And so he's on uh chariot going looking at all the armaments and battalions, making sure everything's right. And God's standing next to him and convinces him that he should do it. And the reason he should do it is because that's his highest fulfillment, that's his purpose, and that's why you should do anything in life. It's not because of money or or power or women or you know, whatever it may be. It's because you are trying to fulfill your ultimate purpose. You are here and you have a relationship with your existence, and that relationship is to fulfill your ultimate purpose. And uh it made me think about all that, and it gave me a smile, and I really appreciate that Hare Krishna gave me those books today. Thanks, y'all.\",\n  \"sentences\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \" Hey everybody, Scotty here.\",\n      \"start\": 0.8,\n      \"end\": 2.64,\n      \"duration\": 1.84,\n      \"confidence\": 0.981,\n      \"tokens\": [\n        {\n          \"text\": \" He\",\n          \"start\": 0.8,\n          \"end\": 1.04,\n          \"duration\": 0.24,\n          \"confidence\": 0.997\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \"y\",\n          \"start\": 1.04,\n          \"end\": 1.12,\n          \"duration\": 0.08,\n          \"confidence\": 0.999\n        },\n        {\n          \"text\": \" ever\",\n          \"start\": 1.2,\n          \"end\